body:
“I’m gayly adjusting my stance so I can go right down the middle.”

“They’re not a part of their body they’re just strap-ons.”

“That was a slow one. Made you think I wasn’t gonna do it then I put it in.”

“I got the octopus, he’s gonna marry me, we’re gonna have tentacle-hooked babies with parrots on the crib.”

“Spank me with a plank and call me poopy Susan.”

“You love a good tentacle don’t you?”
